               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">MARIA ROAKES</hi>. I am an undertaker, and live in Blackman-street, Borough. The prisoner was eight years in my employ as a journeyman—I did not miss this saw till he confessed taking it, and gave up the duplicat in mu parlour—It was after he was charged with stealing the property—we missed several little things, and made inquiries, and he said he took them meaning to replace them again—I had a very good opinion of him.</p>
